    {
      "id": "intro-0",
      "sectionId": "intro",
      "title": "简介",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "提供基本语法和方法的 Elixir 快速参考备忘单。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-1",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "安装 Elixir",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "Elixir 自带了 `iex` 这样一个交互 shell，可以随时计算 Elixir 表达式的值，运行`iex`命令，继续输入几个简单的表达式试试："
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-2",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "shell",
      "code": "iex%202%2B3%0A5%0Aiex%202%2B3%20%3D%3D%205%0Atrue%0Aiex%20String.length(%22%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E7%9A%84%E7%8B%90%E7%8B%B8%E8%B7%B3%E8%BF%87%E4%BA%86%E6%87%92%E6%83%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%8B%97%22)%0A43",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-3",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "每个操作系统的文档可以在[官网](https://elixir-lang.org)网站上 [Installing Elixir](http://elixir-lang.org/install.html) 部分找到"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-4",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "hello.exs",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "IO.puts(%22Hello%20world%20from%20Elixir%22)",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-5",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "Elixir 运行命令"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-6",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "shell",
      "code": "$ elixir hello.exs"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-7",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "基本类型",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "Elixir 支持多种基本类型：整数、浮点、布尔值、原子和字符串。其他数据类型，如列表和元组"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-8",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "%23%20integer%20%E6%95%B4%E6%95%B0%0Aiex%3E%201%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%0A%23%20integer%EF%BC%88%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%812%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E3%80%818%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E5%92%8C16%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%95%B4%E6%95%B0%EF%BC%89%0Aiex%3E%200x1F%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%0A%23%20float%0Aiex%3E%201.0%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%0A%23%20boolean%0Aiex%3E%20true%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%0A%23%20atom%20%2F%20symbol%0Aiex%3E%20%3Aatom%20%20%20%20%20%20%0A%23%20string%0Aiex%3E%20%22elixir%22%20%20%20%0A%23%20list%0Aiex%3E%20%5B1%2C%202%2C%203%5D%20%20%0A%23%20tuple%0Aiex%3E%20%7B1%2C%202%2C%203%7D",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-9",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "注释",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "# 这是一个单行注释"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-10",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E6%8F%92%E5%80%BC%E4%B8%8E%E6%8B%BC%E6%8E%A5",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20name%20%3D%20%22Sean%22%0Aiex%3E%20%22Hello%20%23%7Bname%7D%22%0A%22Hello%20Sean%22%0A%0Aiex%3E%20%22Hello%20%22%20%3C%3E%20%22world!%22%0A%22Hello%20world!%22",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-11",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "变量和模式匹配",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "x = 1\n# => x 现在等于 1\n\n{a, b} = {1, 2}\n# => a 等于 1，b 等于 2"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-12",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "在 Elixir 中，使用 `=` 来进行赋值操作，但实际上是模式匹配。左边是模式，右边是值"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-13",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "原子（Atoms）",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": ":ok"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-14",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "原子是常量，它们的名称就是它们的值"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-15",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "列表（Lists）",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "list = [1, 2, 3]"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-16",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%88Tuples%EF%BC%89",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "tuple%20%3D%20%7B%3Aok%2C%20%22value%22%7D",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-17",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "函数定义",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "defmodule MyModule do\n  def my_function(parameter) do\n    # 函数体\n  end\nend"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-18",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "匿名函数",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "add = fn a, b -> a + b end"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-19",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "控制结构",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "`if/else`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-20",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "if%20x%20%3E%200%20do%0A%20%20%22Positive%22%0Aelse%0A%20%20%22Non-positive%22%0Aend",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-21",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "`case`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-22",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "case%20%7B1%2C%202%7D%20do%0A%20%20%7B1%2C%20x%7D%20-%3E%20%22Matched%20%23%7Bx%7D%22%0A%20%20_%20-%3E%20%22Not%20matched%22%0Aend",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-23",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "`cond`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-24",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "cond%20do%0A%20%20x%20%3E%202%20-%3E%20%22Greater%20than%202%22%0A%20%20x%20%3D%3D%202%20-%3E%20%22Equal%20to%202%22%0A%20%20true%20-%3E%20%22Less%20than%202%22%0Aend",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-25",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "基本算术",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> 1 + 2\n3\niex> 5 * 5\n25\niex> 10 / 2\n5.0"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-26",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "运算符`/`总是返回一个 float。如果你想做整数除法或得到除法余数，你可以调用 div 和 rem 函数:"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-27",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> div(10, 2)\n5"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-28",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "允许在调用需要一个或多个参数的函数时删除括号"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-29",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> div 10, 2 \n5\niex> rem 10, 3\n1"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-30",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "可以调用 round 函数来获取与给定浮点数最接近的整数，或者调用 trunc 函数来获取浮点数的整数部分"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-31",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> round(3.58)\n4\niex> trunc(3.58)\n3"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-32",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "可以使用 is_integer、is_float 或 is_number 分别检查参数是否为 integer、float 或 number 类型"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-33",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> is_integer(1)\ntrue\niex> is_float(2.0)\ntrue\niex> is_number(2.0)\nfalse"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-34",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "布尔算术",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "Elixir 提供了 `||`、`&&` 和 `!` 布尔操作符，它们支持任何类型的操作："
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-35",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> -20 || true\n-20\niex> false || 42\n42\n\niex> 42 && true\ntrue\niex> 42 && nil\nnil\n\niex> !42\nfalse\niex> !false\ntrue"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-36",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "还有三个操作符（and、or、not），它们的第一个参数**必须是布尔类型**（true 和 false）:"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-37",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> true and 42\n42\niex> false or true\ntrue\niex> not false\ntrue\niex> 42 and true\n** (ArgumentError) argument error: 42\niex> not 42\n** (ArgumentError) argument error"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-38",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "模块和函数导入",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "import List, only: [duplicate: 2]"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-39",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "管道操作符",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "result = data\n         |> process1()\n         |> process2()"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-40",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "`|>` 用于链式调用函数，将前一个函数的结果作为下一个函数的第一个参数"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-41",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "比较运算符",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "比较运算符 ：`==`, `!=`, `===`, `!==`, `<=`, `>=`, `<` 和 `>`"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1-42",
      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> 1 > 2\nfalse\niex> 1 != 2\ntrue\niex> 2 == 2\ntrue\niex> 2 <= 3\ntrue"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-43",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "集合",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": ">\n> 列表（list）、元组（tuple）、关键字列表（keyword list）、映射（map）。\n>"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-44",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%88List%EF%BC%89",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20%5B3.14%2C%20%3Apie%2C%20%22Apple%22%5D%0A%5B3.14%2C%20%3Apie%2C%20%22Apple%22%5D%0A%0Aiex%3E%20list%20%3D%20%5B3.14%2C%20%3Apie%2C%20%22Apple%22%5D%0Aiex%3E%20%5B3.14%2C%20%3Apie%2C%20%22Apple%22%5D",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-45",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "列表的开头添加元素"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-46",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20%5B%22%CF%80%22%20%7C%20list%5D%0A%5B%22%CF%80%22%2C%203.14%2C%20%3Apie%2C%20%22Apple%22%5D",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-47",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "列表的尾部添加元素/列表拼接"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-48",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20list%20%2B%2B%20%5B%22Cherry%22%5D%0A%5B3.14%2C%20%3Apie%2C%20%22Apple%22%2C%20%22Cherry%22%5D",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-49",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "获取列表的头部元素"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-50",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20hd%20%5B3.14%2C%20%3Apie%2C%20%22Apple%22%5D%0A3.14",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-51",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "获取列表的尾部元素"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-52",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20tl%20%5B3.14%2C%20%3Apie%2C%20%22Apple%22%5D%0A%5B%3Apie%2C%20%22Apple%22%5D",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-53",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84%EF%BC%88Tuple%EF%BC%89",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20%7B3.14%2C%20%3Apie%2C%20%22Apple%22%7D%0A%7B3.14%2C%20%3Apie%2C%20%22Apple%22%7D",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-54",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E5%AD%97%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%EF%BC%88Keyword%20List%EF%BC%89",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20%5Bfoo%3A%20%22bar%22%2C%20hello%3A%20%22world%22%5D%0A%5Bfoo%3A%20%22bar%22%2C%20hello%3A%20%22world%22%5D%0Aiex%3E%20%5B%7B%3Afoo%2C%20%22bar%22%7D%2C%20%7B%3Ahello%2C%20%22world%22%7D%5D%0A%5Bfoo%3A%20%22bar%22%2C%20hello%3A%20%22world%22%5D",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-55",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "关键字列表非常重要，它有以下的特性："
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-56",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "• 键（key）都是原子（atom）\n• 键（key）是有序的（定义后，顺序不会改变）\n• 键（key）不必是唯一的"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-57",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "因为这些原因，常见的用法是作为参数传递给函数"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-58",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "映射（Map）",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "Elixir 的映射（maps）是键值对结构的第一选择，和关键字列表（keywords）不同，映射允许任意类型的数据作为键，而且数据并不严格排序。 你可以使用 %{} 来定义映射："
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-59",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20map%20%3D%20%25%7B%3Afoo%20%3D%3E%20%22bar%22%2C%20%22hello%22%20%3D%3E%20%3Aworld%7D%0A%25%7B%3Afoo%20%3D%3E%20%22bar%22%2C%20%22hello%22%20%3D%3E%20%3Aworld%7D%0Aiex%3E%20map%5B%3Afoo%5D%0A%22bar%22%0Aiex%3E%20map%5B%22hello%22%5D%0A%3Aworld",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-60",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "模式匹配",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": ">\n> 模式匹配是 Elixir 很强大的特性，它允许我们匹配简单值、数据结构、甚至函数。\n>"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-61",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20%7Ba%2C%20b%2C%20c%7D%20%3D%20%7B%3Ahello%2C%20%22world%22%2C%2042%7D%0A%7B%3Ahello%2C%20%22world%22%2C%2042%7D%0Aiex%3E%20a%0A%3Ahello%0Aiex%3E%20b%0A%22world%22",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-62",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "匹配列表",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "",
      "code": "iex> [a, b, c] = [1, 2, 3]\n[1, 2, 3]\niex> a\n1"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-63",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "匹配列表的头部元素",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "",
      "code": "iex> [head | tail] = [1, 2, 3]\n[1, 2, 3]\niex> head\n1\niex> tail\n[2, 3]"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-64",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "Pin 操作符",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "pin 操作符，就是用已经绑定的值去匹配，而不是重新绑定一个新值。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-65",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> {x, ^x} = {2, 1}\n{2, 1}\niex> x\n2"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-66",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "使用下划线 `_` 忽略匹配的值",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> [head | _] = [1, 2, 3]\n[1, 2, 3]\niex> head\n1"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-67",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "if/else/end",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "if condition do\n  # 条件成立时执行的代码\nelse\n  # 条件不成立时执行的代码\nend"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-68",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "case/end",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "case expression do\n  pattern1 -> # 匹配 pattern1 时执行的代码\n  pattern2 -> # 匹配 pattern2 时执行的代码\n  _ -> # 其他情况执行的代码\nend"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-69",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "cond/end",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "cond do\n  condition1 -> # 条件1成立时执行的代码\n  condition2 -> # 条件2成立时执行的代码\n  true -> # 如果没有任何条件成立，执行这里的代码\nend"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-70",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "unless/do/end",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "unless condition do\n  # 条件为假时执行的代码\nend"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-71",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "try/rescue/end",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "try do\n  # 可能会引发异常的代码\nrescue\n  pattern1 -> # 匹配 pattern1 的异常处理代码\n  pattern2 -> # 匹配 pattern2 的异常处理代码\n  _ -> # 其他异常处理代码\nend"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-72",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "case",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "允许将一个值与许多模式进行比较，直到找到匹配的模式："
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-73",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20case%20%7B1%2C%202%2C%203%7D%20do%0A%20%20%7B4%2C%205%2C%206%7D%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22This%20clause%20won't%20match%22%0A%20%20%7B1%2C%20x%2C%203%7D%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22%E8%AF%A5%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%A5%E5%B0%86%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E5%B9%B6%E7%BB%91%E5%AE%9A%20x%20%E5%88%B0%E8%AF%A5%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%202%22%0A%20%20_%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22This%20clause%20would%20match%20any%20value%22%0Aend%0A%22%E8%AF%A5%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%A5%E5%B0%86%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E5%B9%B6%E7%BB%91%E5%AE%9A%20x%20%E5%88%B0%E8%AF%A5%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%A5%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%202%22",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-74",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "还可以使用when指定额外的条件"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-75",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20case%20%7B1%2C%202%2C%203%7D%20do%0A%20%20%7B1%2C%20x%2C%203%7D%20when%20x%20%3E%200%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22Will%20match%22%0A%20%20_%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%A1%E8%B6%B3%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%86%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%22%0Aend%0A%22Will%20match%22",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-76",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "cond",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "当我们需要根据条件进行匹配而不是值时，类似于其他语言的 `else if` 或 `elsif`，可以使用 `cond` 控制结构。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-77",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20cond%20do%0A%20%202%20%2B%202%20%3D%3D%205%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22This%20will%20not%20be%20true%22%0A%20%202%20*%202%20%3D%3D%203%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22Nor%20this%22%0A%20%201%20%2B%201%20%3D%3D%202%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22But%20this%20will%22%0Aend%0A%22But%20this%20will%22",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-78",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "如果所有的条件都返回 `nil` 或 `false`，则会引发一个错误（CondClauseError）。因此，需要添加一个 `final` 条件，等于 `true`，它将始终匹配："
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-79",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex%3E%20cond%20do%0A%20%202%20%2B%202%20%3D%3D%205%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22This%20is%20never%20true%22%0A%20%202%20*%202%20%3D%3D%203%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22Nor%20this%22%0A%20%20true%20-%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%22%E8%BF%99%E5%A7%8B%E7%BB%88%E4%B8%BA%E7%9C%9F%EF%BC%88%E7%AD%89%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8E%20else%EF%BC%89%22%0Aend%0A%22%E8%BF%99%E5%A7%8B%E7%BB%88%E4%B8%BA%E7%9C%9F%EF%BC%88%E7%AD%89%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8E%20else%EF%BC%89%22",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-80",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "变量的作用域",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "如果在if、case和类似的构造中声明或更改了任何变量，则声明和更改将只在构造中可见。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-81",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> x = 1\n1\nif true do\n  x = x + 1\nend\n2\niex> x\n1"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-82",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "如果要更改值，则必须从if返回值："
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-83",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> x = 1\n1\niex> x = if true do\n  x + 1\nelse\n  x\nend\n2"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-84",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "函数定义",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "def function_name(param1, param2) do\n  # 函数体\nend"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-85",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "示例："
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-86",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "def sum(a, b) do\n  a + b\nend"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-87",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "def%20fun_name(%3Aatom)%20do%0A%20%20%23%20%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%20%3Aatom%20%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%0Aend%0A%0Adef%20fun_name(%22string%22)%20do%0A%20%20%23%20%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%20%22string%22%20%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%0Aend%0A%0Adef%20fun_name(number)%20when%20is_integer(number)%20do%0A%20%20%23%20%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E6%95%B4%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%0Aend",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-88",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "示例："
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-89",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "def is_positive(number) when number > 0 do\n  true\nend\n\ndef is_positive(_), do: false"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-90",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "函数调用",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "module_name.function_name(arg1, arg2)"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-91",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "示例："
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-92",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "Enum.map([1, 2, 3], &(&1 * 2))"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-93",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "函数参数默认值",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "def function_name(parameter \\\\ 默认值) do\n  # 函数体\nend"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-94",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "示例："
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-95",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "def%20greet(name%20%5C%5C%20%22World%22)%20do%0A%20%20%22Hello%2C%20%23%7Bname%7D!%22%0Aend",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-96",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "可变参数数量",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "def function_name(param1, param2 \\\\ []) do\n  # 函数体\nend"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-97",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "示例："
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-98",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "def sum(numbers) do\n  Enum.sum(numbers)\nend"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-99",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E6%B3%A8%E9%87%8A",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "%40doc%20%22%22%22%0A%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E3%80%82%0A%22%22%22",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-100",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "示例："
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-101",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "%40doc%20%22%22%22%0AAdds%20two%20numbers%20together.%0A%0A%23%23%20%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%0A%0A%20%20%20%20iex%3E%20MyModule.add(1%2C%202)%0A%20%20%20%203%0A%22%22%22%0Adef%20add(a%2C%20b)%20do%0A%20%20a%20%2B%20b%0Aend",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-102",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "这些是 Elixir 函数语法的基本要点，可以帮助你开始编写函数。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-103",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "匿名函数",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> sum = fn (a, b) -> a + b end\niex> sum.(2, 3)\n5"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-104",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "可以使用 & 语法来简化匿名函数的定义："
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-105",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> sum = &(&1 + &2)\niex> sum.(2, 3)\n5"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-106",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "闭包",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "匿名函数去引用外部的变量，这通常被称为闭包。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-107",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> double = fn a -> add.(a, a) end\n#Function<6.71889879/1 in :erl_eval.expr/5>\ndouble.(2)\n4"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-108",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "闭包与守卫"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-109",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> f = fn\n  x, y when x > 0 -> x + y\n  x, y -> x * y\nend\n\niex> f.(1, 3)\n4\niex> f.(-1, 3)\n-3"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-110",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "命名函数",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "命名函数是通过 def 关键字定义在某个模块中"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-111",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "defmodule%20Greeter%20do%0A%20%20def%20hello(name)%20do%0A%20%20%20%20%22Hello%2C%20%22%20%3C%3E%20name%0A%20%20end%0Aend%0A%0Aiex%3E%20Greeter.hello(%22Sean%22)%0A%22Hello%2C%20Sean%22",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-112",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "简写为一行："
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-113",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "defmodule%20Greeter%20do%0A%20%20def%20hello(name)%2C%20do%3A%20%22Hello%2C%20%22%20%3C%3E%20name%0Aend",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-114",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "私有函数"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-115",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "defmodule%20Greeter%20do%0A%20%20def%20hello(name)%2C%20do%3A%20phrase%20%3C%3E%20name%0A%20%20%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8defp%E6%9D%A5%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E7%A7%81%E6%9C%89%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%0A%20%20defp%20phrase%2C%20do%3A%20%22Hello%2C%20%22%20%0Aend",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-116",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "函数的默认参数：使用 `\\\\` 来定义默认参数"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-117",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "defmodule%20Greeter%20do%0A%20%20def%20hello(name%2C%20language_code%20%5C%5C%20%22en%22)%20do%0A%20%20%20%20phrase(language_code)%20%3C%3E%20name%0A%20%20end%0A%0A%20%20defp%20phrase(%22en%22)%2C%20do%3A%20%22Hello%2C%20%22%0A%20%20defp%20phrase(%22es%22)%2C%20do%3A%20%22Hola%2C%20%22%0Aend",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-118",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "Enumerables 与 Streams",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": ">\n> Elixir 提供了 Enum 和 Stream 两个模块，用于处理集合。\n>"
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-119",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "Enum",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": ">\n> Enum 模块提供了对集合的常用操作，如 map、filter、reduce、sort、chunk、join、into 等。"
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-120",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> Enum.map([1, 2, 3], fn x -> x * 2 end)\n[2, 4, 6]\niex> Enum.map(%{1 => 2, 3 => 4}, fn {k, v} -> k * v end)\n[2, 12]"
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-121",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "Stream",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": ">\n> 作为Enum的替代品，Elixir提供了支持懒惰操作的Stream模块"
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-122",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "code",
      "lang": "elixir",
      "code": "iex> 1..100_000 |> Stream.map(&(&1 * 3)) |> Stream.filter(odd?) |> Enum.sum()\n7500000000"
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-123",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "",
      "kind": "text",
      "body": "> 流文件操作"
    },
    {
      "id": "s6-124",
      "sectionId": "s6",
      "title": "",
